{
 "name": "RPlog_Not_My_Kind_of_Archaeology_The_Unwelcome_Visitor",
 "title": "Not My Kind of Archaeology: The Unwelcome Visitor",
 "summary": "On the Ord Mantell tarmac, a pleasant exchange between a Mon Calamari Senator, the pilot Leo, and the perpetually unlucky Johanna is interrupted by a shambling, decaying animated corpse, a Sith-puppet delivering a threat about the Jedi's scholars touching their founder's orb. The newly arrived medic Myiari, who has just stepped off a shuttle, is singled out by the creature and pulled toward the group by an unseen Force, ordered to bring all of them to Nar Shaddaa or suffer unimaginable terrors. As the corpse collapses into rot, the veiled freighter captain Brin Harper arrives and helps reassure the shaken Myiari, offering the Jedi's protection. Joined by the cheerful Flight Cadet Joran Hess, the group makes introductions and Brin escorts the newcomers via the transit line to the Jedi Temple.",
